<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She recently celebrated her second wedding anniversary with husband Justin.</p>

<p>And Hailey Bieber put on a very leggy display as she stepped out for lunch with the singer, 26, at Il Pastaio in Beverly Hills, California, on Friday.</p>

<p>The model, 23, kept things casual for her outing and wore an oversized black jumper with matching shorts underneath that highlighted her slender legs. </p>

