<p>Hailey completed her look by wearing a pair of quirky open-toe sandals, while she protected herself amid the coronavirus crisis by wearing a black face mask.</p>

<p>The blonde beauty wore her golden locks in a sleek bun, and she used a light palette of make-up for the occasion.  </p>

